snippet.textDisplay: When I played this as a kid, i never really appreciated the music that was in this game but now as an adult looking at it from a new perspective, i think the composer for this game had an excellent choice in their creation of the game BGMs. This, along with the music for Tarmac Trouble (the level after this) and Final Showdown were my favorite BGMs for the game... although Final Showdown's music was kind of creepy to tell you the truth.
